01:01:24,097 --> 01:01:25,306
Let's think about it.

1022
01:01:34,023 --> 01:01:36,901
After the legislative candidate debate,
the approval rating

1023
01:01:36,984 --> 01:01:39,821
for the nonpartisan Kang Seon-yeong
soared in Seongjin.

1024
01:01:39,904 --> 01:01:42,323
Candidate Kang turned the tables
by revealing

1025
01:01:42,407 --> 01:01:44,701
that relatives of Candidate Jo Nam-gi
purchased lands

1026
01:01:44,784 --> 01:01:47,370
near where the building
of an industrial complex

1027
01:01:47,453 --> 01:01:49,706
has been promised by him.

1028
01:01:50,289 --> 01:01:51,958
Someone once said

1029
01:01:52,542 --> 01:01:54,544
our society has become cold and dark

1030
01:01:55,169 --> 01:01:56,879
and gotten used to others' pain.

1031
01:01:57,463 --> 01:01:59,298
That's where politicians
should be present.

1032
01:02:00,800 --> 01:02:04,429
He said that is the mission
of politicians.

1033
01:02:05,012 --> 01:02:06,431
I will not give up.

1034
01:02:07,265 --> 01:02:09,225
I will stand by your side.

1035
01:02:09,350 --> 01:02:11,728
I will relieve your ongoing pain.

1036
01:02:12,061 --> 01:02:14,981
I will create a better future
to heal your wounds.

1037
01:02:15,064 --> 01:02:17,942
Please give me a chance
to keep my promise.

1038
01:02:19,360 --> 01:02:20,570
I promise you

1039
01:02:20,903 --> 01:02:22,321
a city where your family,

1040
01:02:22,405 --> 01:02:23,823
where your neighbors

1041
01:02:23,906 --> 01:02:25,158
all can get along in harmony.

1042
01:02:25,658 --> 01:02:28,870
I will make Seongjin a city

1043
01:02:29,871 --> 01:02:31,581
anyone and everyone wants to live in.

1044
01:02:32,206 --> 01:02:34,167
Considering the little time left,

1045
01:02:34,250 --> 01:02:37,628
Candidate Kang is most likely
to win the election.

1046
01:02:38,212 --> 01:02:39,589
Oh, hello.

1047
01:02:41,466 --> 01:02:44,385
-Thank you for making time for me.
-No problem.

1048
01:02:48,514 --> 01:02:51,392
I'm wondering why the Chief
Presidential Secretary wants to see me.

1049
01:02:51,476 --> 01:02:56,647
As you may know,
the President is in a bit of trouble.

1050
01:02:57,231 --> 01:02:59,233
Many of the plans
he's been pushing ahead with

1051
01:02:59,358 --> 01:03:00,818
are falling through.

1052
01:03:00,902 --> 01:03:03,654
It seems the ruling party
will most likely fail

1053
01:03:03,738 --> 01:03:07,742
to win the majority
in the legislative election.

1054
01:03:08,910 --> 01:03:09,952
That's right.

1055
01:03:12,163 --> 01:03:14,165
I'll be straightforward with you.

1056
01:03:15,583 --> 01:03:19,796
Please come to the Blue House
aid the President.

1057
01:03:28,262 --> 01:03:31,474
If I enter the Blue House after being
investigated by the prosecution,

1058
01:03:32,934 --> 01:03:34,268
it'll cause quite a stir.

1059
01:03:35,019 --> 01:03:36,521
We're prepared for that.

1060
01:03:37,104 --> 01:03:39,649
We're also aware
that you had good intentions.

1061
01:03:40,358 --> 01:03:41,400
But,

1062
01:03:42,318 --> 01:03:43,694
why me, of all people?

1063
01:03:44,946 --> 01:03:46,322
You can ask him directly.

1064
01:03:47,240 --> 01:03:48,366
Ask who?

1065
01:03:49,283 --> 01:03:50,493
The President

1066
01:03:51,369 --> 01:03:53,162
chose you himself.

1067
01:03:54,497 --> 01:03:57,041
He'll give you a call soon.

1068
01:03:58,543 --> 01:03:59,710
Well...

1069
01:04:01,462 --> 01:04:02,463
Thank you.

1070
01:04:34,328 --> 01:04:38,165
One light can't light up the night.

1071
01:04:46,340 --> 01:04:51,220
Deepening darkness can sometimes
only be fought with darkness.

1072
01:04:53,931 --> 01:04:58,853
Yet I must keep my light alive
even in the dangerous darkness.

1073
01:05:02,732 --> 01:05:04,650
As I wait for daybreak,

1074
01:05:07,695 --> 01:05:11,115
I must keep shining my light endlessly.

1075
01:05:18,706 --> 01:05:22,710
There is only one path for me.

1076
01:05:24,837 --> 01:05:26,047
This is Jang Tae-jun.

1077
01:06:41,372 --> 01:06:45,126
THANK YOU FOR WATCHING
CHIEF OF STAFF SEASON 2

